; This has been extracted from
; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/gotty.md

% gotty, common

# Share result of command
gotty <command>

# Share with write permission
gotty <__w___permit_write_> <shell>

# Share with credential (Basic Auth)
gotty <__w___permit_write_> <__c___credential_> <username>:<password> <shell>
